Logistics Software Development

In today’s tech-driven world, adopting enterprise mobility solutions is no longer an optional advantage; it’s a necessity. Especially in the logistics industry, where numerous vehicles and drivers are involved in transporting consignments, mobility solutions are imperative for reliability and productivity. Hashlogics understands the pivotal role mobility plays, empowering drivers, facility managers, and service professionals with mobile devices and apps. Our logistics app allows customers to track vehicle positions in real-time, make online payments, provide feedback, and access 24/7 support.

Comprehensive Logistics and Transportation Software Development Solutions

We specialize in building, customizing, and seamlessly integrating transport and logistics software that handles every facet of your supply chain. From manufacturer order processing to inventory management, shipment tracking, and distribution, we have got you covered.

Advanced Logistics and Shipping Software

Our expert developers create AI-driven shipping logistics management software to optimize routes, improve supply chain visibility, and streamline scheduling operations. We incorporate logistics ERP and CRM software, GPS tracking, cloud-based platforms, fleet management software, and more.

Warehouse Management Systems (WMS)

We integrate your WMS with a comprehensive SCM platform, enabling access to warehouse stock arrangements, shipment tracking, and real-time data from a single interface. Our solutions cover inventory management, labor and yard management, cross-docking support, and more.

Freight and Shipping

We tailor freight and shipping modules to your specific needs for TL, LTL, and Intermodal Freight Operations. Our backend algorithms allow you to access third-party shipping provider data, generate shipping labels, perform direct rate comparisons, and make precise forecasts.

Enhanced Supply Chain Management (SCM)

We enhance your SCM system with cloud-based software to boost communication, monitoring, logistics management, transportation management, and automation. Integration options include WMS, Machine Learning Software, Cold Chain Management Systems, IoT Fleet Monitoring, ERP, Blockchain Technology, CRM, and more.

Freight Broker Software

We seamlessly integrate your existing Freight Broker Software to optimize lead generation, competitor analysis, GPS and satellite tracking, and communication via SMS or voice-over IP with platforms like Twilio. We also enhance GPS and satellite tracking using Google Maps.

Efficient Order Processing

Our Shipping Transportation Software Development Company excels in optimizing order processing within tailored SCM systems. We seamlessly integrate E-Commerce Storefronts, Payment Gateway Systems, and Reverse Logistics Modules to enhance the efficient management of purchase orders.

Get Started!

E-Commerce Automation

At Hashlogics, we specialize in crafting tailored E-Commerce Automation Software, specifically designed for custom software development for logistics. Our solutions empower you with multi-channel inventory control, streamlined order fulfillment and processing, and expedited shipping, all aimed at enhancing customer satisfaction and team efficiency. Through E-Commerce Automation, you can automate routine tasks using algorithms that identify predefined triggers and desired actions, leading to substantial time and cost savings while minimizing the need for manual intervention.

Get Started!

For BigCommerce

Hashlogics seamlessly integrates various Shipping and logistics Software, such as Shippo, into your BigCommerce storefront, helping you minimize shipping expenses across carriers like USPS, UPS, DHL, and more.

For Shopify

We facilitate the synchronization of orders from your Shopify application with your existing Logistics and shipping Software, like ShipHawk, streamlining and centralizing the fulfillment process for your convenience.

For Magento

Our solutions simplify freight shipping by integrating your current Magento e-commerce platform with a Transportation Management System (TMS) like Shipwell, providing you with a competitive edge in the market.

FedEx

We seamlessly integrate FedEx software with certified solutions like QuickBooks and NetSuite, facilitating the growth of your business on both domestic and international fronts

UPS

Our developers establish a seamless connection between UPS shipping solutions and your existing Transportation Management System (TMS), ensuring effortless integration with ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning), WMS (Warehouse Management System), and accounting systems.

United States Postal Service (USPS)

We provide comprehensive integration of Multi-Carrier, LTL, TL, and Private-Fleet Shipping Solutions with USPS Software, addressing all your transportation management and supply chain execution needs.

Third-Party Shipping Integration

Our adept team of Shipping and Logistics Management Software Developers excels in crafting customized transportation logistics software, finely tuned to automate and optimize the entire transportation management process. This includes efficient shipment processing, real-time tracking, and vigilant monitoring of carrier performance, spanning parcel, TL (Truckload), LTL (Less-Than-Truckload) carriers, and more.

Choose Hashlogics for your logistics software development needs!

Features of Our Custom Logistics Software Development

In the process of crafting a freight and logistics software app, it’s crucial to incorporate these highlighted features. Beyond these, our developers adeptly integrate additional functionalities based on individual client needs.

  • User Accounts
  • Seamless GPS Integration
  • Offline Functionality
  • Shipment Tracking
  • Vehicle and Driver Monitoring
  • Comprehensive Reporting
  • Optimized Driving Routes
  • Real-time Communication
  • Automated Order Dispatch

Process Involved in Our Transportation Software Development

Mapping Integrations

  • Optimized Driving Routes

We seamlessly integrate the Waze API with your customized Supply Chain Management (SCM) system, granting access to real-time, turn-by-turn navigation on current road conditions.

  • Google Maps

Through Google Maps, we implement Geographic Information System (GIS) map layer solutions, providing detailed and optimized map navigation in real-time.

  • ArcGIS

We incorporate ArcGIS integrations for storing and managing crucial geospatial information, including maps and data.

Real-Time Tracking & Monitoring

At Hashlogics, we integrate IoT-enabled Real-Time GPS Tracking Systems into your SCM infrastructure, enabling comprehensive monitoring of fleets, shipments, deliveries, fuel supply, and more. Our software solutions optimize transit time, route planning, product integrity, and equipment damage control, and incorporate RFID/QR Code scanner tools, telematics, and more.

ERP Integration

We seamlessly merge your ERP with the supply chain, enhancing data management across all levels for increased transparency and operational efficiency. Our Logistics Management System integrates tools for order management, processing, reverse logistics, Electronic Proof of Delivery (EPOD), route optimization, and more.

Advanced Analytics

Leveraging big data analytics software, Hashlogics empowers operations managers to pinpoint and eliminate bottlenecks that impede SCM processes. We integrate third-party manufacturing software and synchronization technologies, such as Synchrono, into your SCM system, effectively identifying and resolving production bottlenecks and managing manufacturing constraints within your Supply Chain Network (SCN). Choose Hashlogics to revolutionize your logistics and shipping processes.
